          <p>We have an RSS feed which allows you to keep up-to-date with recent additions to Mutopia without having to visit the website to find out if anything's been added. The URL is: <a href="latestadditions.rss">http://www.mutopiaproject.org/latestadditions.rss</a></p>

          <p>More information on RSS and how to use it is available on the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RSS">Wikipedia RSS page</a>.</p>
        </div>

